}
\par \pard\plain \s21\sb0\sa120{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\lang2057
The characterisation of Appellant\'92s relationship with its farmer members as a single economic entity is problematic. The concept of a single economic entity is only to be found in Section 4 of the Act, the }
