The Tribunal states further that:}
\par \pard\plain \s21\sb0\sa120\qj{\rtlch \ltrch
\'93}{\b\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Sub-section 4(5) ensures that agreements between firms that are related to each other in the fashion described will not be hit by the prohibition of the horizontal agreements described }
